Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.63,0:00:02.30,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Perceiving in a flash,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.63,0:00:03.63,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Once it starts, it won't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.25,0:00:05.42,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today's stage is the police headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.84,0:00:07.09,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Police officers are people, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:09.05,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They're always busy with cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:10.97,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Seeing the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.26,0:00:12.89,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A child with an adult's intelligence...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.43,0:00:15.35,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.56,0:01:39.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Metropolitan Police Officer Love Story: Part One!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.65,0:01:50.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the police headquarters? It's big.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.78,0:01:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They must deal with a lot of cases here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.82,0:01:58.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, this place is the parent to all of Japan's police.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:00.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.16,0:02:07.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now now, we're only here as witnesses to the blue castle case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:10.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're not here to have a picnic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.30,0:02:12.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even you were excited, saying you wanted\Nto hear about some unsolved cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.01,0:02:20.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right! The one anticipating this the most was Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:22.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.23,0:02:24.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.27,0:02:27.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Relay your statements in my absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:29.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:31.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're Agasa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.59,0:02:35.98,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Takagi Wataru\NInvestigation Division Police Officer - 1st Division
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:34.40,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's nice to meet you, I'm Takagi from the first division.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.16,0:02:37.16,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Just follow me, everyone this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.74,0:02:38.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:45.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize for your trip here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.96,0:02:46.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:48.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This place is pretty clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:50.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This place is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.80,0:02:55.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it would be disorganized and filled with cigarette smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:02:57.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They only made it look nice out here, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.85,0:03:00.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right right, I bet the officers' quarters must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.31,0:03:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This place seems empty...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:13.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You all seem surprised, is it really that surprising?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:18.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, thought the officers' quarters would\Nbe filled with cigarette smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:23.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I expected scary middle aged men to glare at us as we entered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:26.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You all have been watching too many police dramas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:28.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, I'm an officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:30.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He doesn't look very strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:33.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He doesn't look like he could apprehend a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.42,0:03:36.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's definitely not popular with the women.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:40.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, where's Inspector Megure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:42.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We came at his request...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:46.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Inspector is working on the bank robbery case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:52.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you mean the 200 million yen stolen at the\Nbank around the Haido area three days ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:53.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:58.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, the Inspector's wife, Midori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, was inside the bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:00.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was wounded by the criminals who pushed her around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.91,0:04:04.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the Inspector is taking it very seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:09.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you have to replace him to take our testimony?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:10.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.67,0:04:14.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's head to the other room to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:17.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's another appointment at 5:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:20.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, the button on your cuff is falling off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:22.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.31,0:04:24.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your collar isn't well cleaned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:27.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your shirt is also wrinkled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.52,0:04:29.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be, Officer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:31.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have no girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:37.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, allow me to introduce\Nyou to my sister's granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:39.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.95,0:04:42.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I actually like someone already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:45.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:48.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with these children?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:51.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For lost kids, it's the lost children department.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:53.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's not, these kids are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:55.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is this lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:57.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:04:58.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you blushing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:00.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.47,0:05:03.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Officer Takagi's lover!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:04.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:08.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it right to bring your lover to your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.73,0:05:09.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:11.94,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,My name is Sato Miwako.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:17.02,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Sato Miwako\NViolent Crimes Unit Police Officer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:16.90,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Even though I'm a female, I'm also from the\N1st Division, in the Violent Crimes Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.99,0:05:19.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A female officer...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:21.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, who are these kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:27.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They are witnesses for that blue castle case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:31.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? So these are those brave kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:32.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The suspect confessed everything, so we asked\Nthem to confirm the background of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:40.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! I remember now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:45.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onee{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you're that officer from the stadium case!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.22,0:05:51.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were awesome back then, Onee{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:55.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. You were the children running around then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:58.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We weren't just running around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.61,0:06:00.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were assisting the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.07,0:06:02.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We didn't interfere with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:06.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right Our detective group is for justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:07.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:09.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:10.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:13.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The stadium case, and the blue castle case,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Might have been solved thanks to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.34,0:06:21.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, boy. Remember this:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:26.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Justice isn't something you can just proclaim.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:31.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a feeling you should keep near your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.98,0:06:34.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you understand, little detectives?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:36.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.61,0:06:38.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that too harsh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:42.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, but wait, Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:49.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you supposed to be investigating the 200\Nmillion yen robbery case with Inspector Megure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:51.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That case brought me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.79,0:06:56.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I received a call from the bank's manager last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.92,0:06:59.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he had something he wanted to discuss with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we decided to meet here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:04.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both of them at 2:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.76,0:07:06.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why both of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.22,0:07:10.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the incident happened, the wife was also present.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:13.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She had a gun held to her by the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.73,0:07:16.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe she remembered something about the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.44,0:07:18.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, that's odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:22.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last night I received a similar call from the bank manager's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:25.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wanted to tell me something she\Nremembered about the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:28.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So she would come alone at 5:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:31.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, the bank manager also mentioned that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:35.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's afraid the criminal may attack his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:37.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he wants to come during the day with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:40.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:46.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, has Yumi from the traffic department told you anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:51.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember drinking with her last night and telling her something...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.39,0:07:53.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I can't recall what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:57.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No, she hasn't said anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:07:59.86,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Listen, listen Takagi{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-kun{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:04.15,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Last night, let her drink, and she told me she has one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:06.03,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She told me she really likes someone in the 1st Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:11.82,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You may be the one, may be! You're blushing, how cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:20.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer Sato, I've brought the manager of the bank as requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.34,0:08:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your trouble. Please join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.32,0:08:28.88,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Masuo Keizou (53)\NTokyo Bank Branch Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:28.88,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It seems I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:31.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, your wife isn't with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:34.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had something to do at the bank,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:37.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I arranged to meet my wife here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.81,0:08:39.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She hasn't made it yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:39.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:43.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange. Is she still asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:47.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, may I use the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:48.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:08:58.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the third time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:00.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.92,0:09:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The amount of times he looked at his watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:09.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Masuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.47,0:09:11.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.51,0:09:15.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh, you're at the police station?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.85,0:09:17.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll put an officer on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:23.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello. You're now speaking with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:27.23,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Masuo Kayo\NWife of Masuo Keizou
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.11,0:09:25.70,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're that officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:27.23,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, I believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:28.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:31.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I assume you're still at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:32.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:34.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.12,0:09:36.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't the appointment at 5:00?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:41.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, your husband said the appointment was at 2:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.67,0:09:43.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we assumed you were coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:45.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't told about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:47.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:50.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, what are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:09:56.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:09:57.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:09:59.69,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Are you there, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:01.61,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's wrong, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:04.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, prepare the mobile team.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:06.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll get the car ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:08.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.90,0:10:09.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mobile team?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:11.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're the ones deployed for a field case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:13.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're called the mobile investigation team.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:15.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.12,0:10:17.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:18.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:26.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My wife is fine, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:28.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As of late,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.59,0:10:30.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you noticed anything suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:32.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:34.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:38.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said she saw someone suspicious outside last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That must be one of the criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:47.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fearing identification by your wife, they're wanting to silence her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:48.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:52.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It may have been a petty thief that caused her to scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.99,0:10:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was speaking with the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't she shout "thief" if it were so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:10:59.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When did you get in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:01.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.91,0:11:03.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no time to take him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:05.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have to check on the woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:07.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boy, don't bite your tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.48,0:11:28.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Kayo? Kayo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.69,0:11:30.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer, please head upstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:32.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll head to the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.28,0:11:34.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.53,0:11:34.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:48.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There is glass missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:51.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Did someone break in?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:54.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:57.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kayo... Kayo...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:03.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:05.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll call an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:10.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, call for the lab team and the coroner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:13.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How... How is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:17.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:20.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,14 hours, 46 minutes. Body discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:20.70,Signs,,0,0,0,,Translator Note: Takagi said the time in Military time as\N14 hours, 46 minutes. This translates to 2:46 P.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:23.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who could be so evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:26.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it really those criminals, Officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:28.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:31.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}When you enter...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.84,0:12:34.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The lady's body is in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:36.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Though, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.34,0:12:42.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Before I discovered the damaged glass,\Nand before telling them to go upstairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:44.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He didn't say anything of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.27,0:12:46.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:53.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Regardless, is it normal to attack someone using a phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.32,0:12:58.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Without caution, the attacker's voice may be overheard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:03.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The other person on the phone would\Ncome to the victim's aid immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.16,0:13:09.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then, his peculiar actions and words at the police headquarters...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.21,0:13:13.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is it possible he planned this murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:16.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is it possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.68,0:13:26.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim is Masuo Kayo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, age 42.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:30.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murder weapon is a knife to the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:34.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no indication as to struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:36.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That wound must have been fatal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:40.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The estimated time of her death is when she screamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:43.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer Sato, you heard the victim scream?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.07,0:13:48.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The husband was at headquarters speaking\Nwith the victim over the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.87,0:13:52.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I accidentally switched to the loudspeaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:54.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.59,0:13:57.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard my wife's cry for help...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:04.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, during the phone conversation,\Nsomeone assaulted her from behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:07.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't believe she was only talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.14,0:14:12.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She must have been riding this aerobic\Nbike while being on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:14.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so, look here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.65,0:14:18.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's sweat on her body and shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:21.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since all metabolic processes cease after death,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:23.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even a high temperature wouldn't cause sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:27.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sweat has yet to dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:31.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means, before the victim was killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:34.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was partaking in a demanding activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:41.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I searched the shoe cabinet and didn't see any jogging shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.76,0:14:44.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And in this room, the only thing capable...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.93,0:14:48.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The electric bike near the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.14,0:14:52.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, children shouldn't be near crime scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:54.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.65,0:14:59.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boy, I still don't know your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:02.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Edogawa Conan, a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:04.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.91,0:15:09.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, he's the boy staying with Detective Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:10.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how you know these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:16.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well boy, you should become a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you make it to our unit, we'll treat you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.63,0:15:22.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:24.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.18,0:15:28.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well Officer Sato, we'll speak with the neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:30.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps there's a witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:34.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, don't forget to investigate this residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:36.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The motive may be money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.77,0:15:37.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.81,0:15:41.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, this doesn't relate to greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.53,0:15:47.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The criminal's target was the life of this woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:49.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's my opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:52.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Secondary Inspector Shiratori...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.25,0:15:54.71,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not a secondary inspector any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.56,0:15:58.04,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Shiratori Ninzaburou\NPolice Inspector - 1st Division
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:57.83,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I've been promoted to full inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.13,0:16:02.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thus I will be assuming control of this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:04.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not bad. You're adept at fawning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:06.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Always getting promotions...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:12.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind, please allow me to assist in the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.47,0:16:13.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:18.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Does that means Sato{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} actually likes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.40,0:16:22.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Shiratori{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:25.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No way, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:28.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}How can I get so distracted while being on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:32.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, how do you know it isn't a simple theft?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:35.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because of the scream during the telephone conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.71,0:16:41.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Normally, a thief wouldn't attack someone who is on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:45.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she saw the thief and screamed, he would have fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:51.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so, wasn't the victim supposed to\Nvisit the police headquarters today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:56.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she sad it was in regards to the bank robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:59.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was supposed to come with her husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:02.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But she didn't show up at the appointed time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.65,0:17:05.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The husband was worried, so he called her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.95,0:17:14.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the phone call, did she happen to\Nmention she was talking to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:19.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She noticed, when I took the phone,\Nthat I was the officer from last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:21.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then there's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:28.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The criminal didn't want the victim to speak\Nwith the police, and thus murdered her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:30.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:34.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, the criminal must be one of the two bank thieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:38.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the incident, the victim was held at gunpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:41.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That would place her near one of the thieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.81,0:17:45.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe the criminal realized she could identity him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.86,0:17:49.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And murdered her to keep her quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:52.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, when the victim was taken hostage...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.66,0:17:56.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She struggled to get away and grabbed at the intruder's mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.45,0:18:03.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, and by coincidence Megure's wife became\Nthe second hostage at the bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:09.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She even volunteered to be a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:15.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! My wife told me about a foreigner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:17.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:22.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe the lady was attempting to refer a clue to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.27,0:18:25.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, contact headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:28.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of the criminals is foreign!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.03,0:18:29.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.74,0:18:31.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But isn't it strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:37.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Behind the bike, there's only two meters of space.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:40.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no door beyond it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:44.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would the criminal attack from that\Ndirection while she was riding the bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.83,0:18:46.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's that kid again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.34,0:18:47.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.42,0:18:52.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's always following Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:53.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A little detective, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:57.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you were famous, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:04.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:05.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:10.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't you think it's strange, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:12.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.99,0:19:17.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you're stabbed in the back, the attack\Ndoesn't always originate from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:19.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's possible the victim saw the criminal,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:23.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And was about to flee when she was stabbed in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:28.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's true, the body would be further\Naway from the electronic vehicle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.09,0:19:30.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The telephone lies only a few inches away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:35.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she fell elsewhere, there would be traces of sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.93,0:19:41.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the criminal would have no reason to move the bike, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:45.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You do have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:49.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Masuo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, did your wife usually ride the bike during this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.44,0:19:55.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Each day at 2:00 she would exercise on that bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.53,0:19:59.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse my asking, but at what time does she normally wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:04.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm always required to leave early due to my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:09.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More recently though, my wife has began drinking\Nout with some friends and returning late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:11.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would gauge it around noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:15.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I have the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:18.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If my reasoning is correct...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.97,0:20:21.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The criminal was hiding...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.93,0:20:24.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the shelf behind the curtains!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.60,0:20:25.06,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:28.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey hey, this is convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:30.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There aren't many books.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.57,0:20:33.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's possible for a person to hide here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:36.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There aren't many other obstructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.07,0:20:40.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only this single curtain is, unlike the others, beige in color.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:44.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The curtain is meant to modify the color\Nscheme, and was installed just recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.70,0:20:48.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were a so planning to change the other curtains...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.21,0:20:53.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But can it really conceal a person?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.09,0:20:58.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you remove two pieces, an adult could easily hide here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.47,0:21:02.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As you see, that is what the criminal did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.56,0:21:07.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The criminal observed the residents' schedules.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:10.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And with the master gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.06,0:21:13.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He snuck in before the lady awoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.36,0:21:19.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He then concealed himself in the shelf\Nand awaited his murder victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:25.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the victim on the bike, her back was unguarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.75,0:21:29.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, his plans were foiled slightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.46,0:21:34.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For better or worse, the police called.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.46,0:21:40.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The anxious criminal quickly committed the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.21,0:21:44.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The criminal entered through the window with the missing glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.22,0:21:51.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. The wife had claimed to witness\Nsomeone suspicious in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.77,0:21:55.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he familiarized himself with her living habits...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.11,0:21:56.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.53,0:22:01.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No. There's a large flaw in that deduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.53,0:22:05.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That man is the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.99,0:22:08.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}From the police headquarters ten kilometers away...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.71,0:22:11.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}To kill his wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.42,0:22:13.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There must be a way to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.97,0:23:48.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's only one person...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.93,0:23:55.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who could restore the bookshelf to its original condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.44,0:24:01.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Impossible! Regardless, you can't just accuse people without proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.99,0:24:09.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Uncle? What's this wound on your finger from?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.08,0:24:10.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.49,0:24:14.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Metropolitan Police Officer Love Story: Part Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.12,0:24:18.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.86,0:24:19.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bookshelf
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.63,0:24:21.55,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next is the finale!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.80,0:24:24.60,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}... tell me it isn't true...
